story of "Right Hand, Left Hand--"

200
00:17:57,540 --> 00:17:59,500
the story of good and evil?

201
00:18:00,500 --> 00:18:02,460
"H-A-T-E."

202
00:18:02,580 --> 00:18:04,660
It was with this left hand
that old Brother Cain...

203
00:18:04,780 --> 00:18:07,220
