Birds will sing

693
00:59:21,180 --> 00:59:23,420
In yonder

694
00:59:23,500 --> 00:59:25,900
Willow

695
00:59:25,980 --> 00:59:29,740
Hush, my little one

696
00:59:29,820 --> 00:59:32,300
Hush

697
00:59:33,540 --> 00:59:36,140
Are we going home now, John?

698
00:59:46,020 --> 00:59:49,780
Rest, dearest one

699
00:59:49,900 --> 00:59:52,620
Rest

700
00:59:54,060 --> 00:59:56,420
Rest here

701
