01:17:12,940 --> 01:17:15,980
What a f ellowship

901
01:17:16,100 --> 01:17:19,260
What a joy divine

902
01:17:19,340 --> 01:17:24,180
Leaning on the Everlasting Arms

903
01:17:24,300 --> 01:17:27,300
What a blessedness

904
01:17:27,380 --> 01:17:31,180
What a peace is mine

905
01:17:31,300 --> 01:17:36,940
Leaning on the Everlasting Arms

906
01:17:37,020 --> 01:17:40,060
- Leaning on Jesus
- Leaning

907
01:17:43,540 --> 01:17:47,500
Saf e and secure from all

908
01:17:47,620 --> 01:17:50,220
Alarms

